name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On January 20, the Ministry of Agriculture said: In 2024, grain production will reach a new level, farmers' income will grow steadily, and rural society will be harmonious and stable.
On January 13, Inner Mongolia. The woman said that her father spent a year planting peppers, but only sold more than 5,000 kilograms for more than 9,000 yuan. In order to lower the price, the merchants who collect peppers deliberately waited until the peppers became particularly dry and light before coming to collect them.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Late-night news! Another real estate boss was arrested, Ou Zongrong, the actual controller of Zhenrong Real Estate, was arrested
The last real estate boss arrested for suspected crimes was Xu Jiayin.
Zhenrong Real Estate Announcement: Recently learned that Ou Zongrong has been taken compulsory measures in accordance with the law for suspected crimes.
An informed source revealed that it was related to an old matter of land auction in Fuzhou more than ten years ago, and it also involved several private real estate companies. But the specific situation is still waiting for further official news.
